Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:21.84,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought that maybe I could \Nget it to move, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:27.74,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:36.41,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:39.08,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:43.97,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,You're always staring at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:45.36,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,It's plain as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:48.39,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,B-But he's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:50.38,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,He's married?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:51.23,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:53.51,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Then you still have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:55.93,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,You've got quite the \Nset of weapons there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:58.47,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:00:59.90,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:03.47,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:06.53,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ari and Maddarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:11.25,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what we agreed upon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.93,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,It was said that I could \Nwatch over them...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:15.22,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:15.94,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:17.46,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:19.39,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:20.34,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.39,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,The committee decided that they
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:26.26,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,want to reevaluate what \Nto do with you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.00,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:05.03,Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}Escape Through the Sewer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.58,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Once we pass over this range,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.14,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be in elf territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.97,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,That means we could be assaulted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.83,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,by the elven army at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.73,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:23.56,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,You have to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.06,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,We Undine Knights will fight and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:26.70,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:27.89,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,We will just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:34.39,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,The strength that the Ostland gains \Nfrom running on steam is her speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.59,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,We'll run and run and run some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:38.83,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:39.56,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.38,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll go their capital, Adil,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.60,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,and locate Saito and Miss Westwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.55,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.70,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,The faster we get to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.94,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,the higher the chance \Nthat they are still safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:51.24,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.08,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.01,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're still okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.25,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're coming for you, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.56,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:06.77,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:11.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bidalsha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.13,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,If you harm Tiffa in any way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:14.87,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.43,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.61,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,just endure it, no matter what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:23.17,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,So this is her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.48,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,She has our elven blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.55,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,but she gained the power of the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.70,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,How truly frightening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:34.40,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful around Eshmael.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.85,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,He's known for hating \Nbarbarians the most
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.66,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,among the elders of the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.55,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,When those who wield \Nthe power of the demon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.01,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,and their familiars gather,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.86,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,four and four in number,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:50.25,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,the Spiritual Continent \Nwill be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.81,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody knows this \N6000 year old prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.67,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the barbarians are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:58.74,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,busy gathering those who \Nwield the demon power,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:01.10,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,and this time, they will not stop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.36,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,until they've destroyed us elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.24,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.70,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,There is one thing we can do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.99,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,before the nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.99,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,of 6000 years ago is repeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.38,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,That is to kill these demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.40,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,thus preventing the four and \Nfour from being united!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.74,CRZero,Voices,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:15.96,CRZero,Voices,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them, kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:19.77,CRZero,Elf1,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, how are we any \Nbetter than the barbarians?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:21.18,CRZero,Elf2,0000,0000,0000,,Locking them away would
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:23.20,CRZero,Elf2,0000,0000,0000,,be enough to keep the four \Nand four from uniting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:24.91,CRZero,Elf3,0000,0000,0000,,He's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.39,CRZero,Elf3,0000,0000,0000,,We elves are a noble race and—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.77,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:31.56,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,If it was only the barbarians, \NI could potentially accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.54,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,But to think that one who looks like us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.31,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,carries the power of the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.35,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,Like this corrupted girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:42.04,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.61,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,My blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:02.38,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,You all saw the foul ways \Nof these barbarians.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.24,CRZero,Eshmael,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still dispute the \Nneed to kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.33,CRZero,Elf1,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.85,CRZero,Elf1,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:12.05,CRZero,Elf1,0000,0000,0000,,Kill, kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.56,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.01,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.04,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.75,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you for standing up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.53,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.38,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.02,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:51.60,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.75,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:57.73,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,But they're doing this \Nbecause I'm a half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.84,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, leave me here and run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:08.41,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you could make \Nit if you were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.65,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.59,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.99,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.45,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought I was just jealous,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.23,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,because Louise had found \Na dependable familiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.23,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,but now I know that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:39.55,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I'm around you, \Nmy heart beats so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.81,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,That means I love you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.22,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:50.30,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I know I shouldn't, but just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.62,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Just once will be enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.87,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:18.05,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Saito? Saito? Saito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.83,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:28.69,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So I was summoned back when you did
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,the Summoning Ceremony in Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.95,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:36.83,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like you had \Nappeared from the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.90,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,But I figured that wasn't possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.23,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,since you are Louise's familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've never heard of anyone \Nbeing two people's familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.51,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.74,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, these runes did appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:54.53,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what these mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:57.96,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:08:59.64,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be all depressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.56,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like you're doing \Npretty well for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:06.09,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Derf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.72,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.36,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a very warm welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.32,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,to those who came to help you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:13.92,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.95,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to guard Bidalsha and Lukshana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.35,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them absolutely \Ninsisted on doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.39,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.09,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:47.05,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! Malicorne spotted an elven ship \Nwith his far sight magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.08,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:49.80,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,He said he saw only one ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.90,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's a patrol ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:55.49,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche, set the steam \Nengines to full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.54,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:58.59,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,We'll accelerate and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:02.11,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,If we do get attacked, I'm \Ncounting on you, Miss Zerbst.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:03.80,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.34,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Just threaten them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:08.24,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't come here to wage war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:10.29,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I understand completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.13,CRZero,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,An unidentified ship is \Napproaching from the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.43,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.33,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a barbarian ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.35,CRZero,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a merchant ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:22.52,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:25.86,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,A merchant ship can't move that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:26.80,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the artillery!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:32.41,CRZero,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:34.01,CRZero,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,We won't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.01,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around and follow that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:44.70,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,Alert others in the area for backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.02,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,Scramble the dragon riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:03.11,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle designed this sewer \Nsystem when he was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:06.70,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,He knows all of these \Npassageways by heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this isn't a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.78,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for trusting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.79,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're the ones who \Nabducted us in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:17.58,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:20.00,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I only participated in this \Nfor research purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:21.76,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Not to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:26.45,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see why my uncle \Nwas against it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.91,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he saw something \Nlike this coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:30.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,He was against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.50,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I did suspect that upon seeing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.66,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,many of our comrades would not be able
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.87,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,to keep their hatred in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.30,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,The history of violence
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.23,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,between the barbarians \Nand us is just too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:45.42,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it could work if we \Nkept you secluded in her oasis,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:48.16,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,but then Eshmael overruled everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:51.61,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you take Joseph's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.88,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Out of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:54.83,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:58.06,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,When we heard that the \Ndemon powers had returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.00,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I approached Joseph to \Ninvestigate it further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:04.40,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I needed to understand the \Ntruth behind this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:08.04,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you did those \Nhorrible things to Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.44,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,It was his condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:12.40,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,If we wanted his cooperation, \Nwe had to bow to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.97,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I knew that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:19.02,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,the true terror was not \Nin this power alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:21.76,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,but in the hearts of those \Nwho wielded such power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.76,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Like the fire stones that were used \Nfor peaceful purposes in Neftes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:28.09,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,In Joseph's hands, they became \Nweapons of mass destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:31.03,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I will never
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.97,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,use the power of the Void
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:36.50,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,for a negative purpose \Nor to hurt people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:39.58,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Louise would never do \Nsomething like that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:40.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I can guarantee it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.14,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:54.08,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Once you exit this door, \Nyou'll be just outside the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.10,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,You can use the dragons to cross \Nthe desert and return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.51,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.17,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,They expected this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.96,CRZero,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,It was Bidalsha who tried
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.31,CRZero,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,to help them escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.00,CRZero,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.44,CRZero,Esmile,0000,0000,0000,,You've sealed the sewers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:16.39,CRZero,Esmile,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only place \Nthat he could run to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:18.92,CRZero,Esmile,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have imagined that I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.41,CRZero,Esmile,0000,0000,0000,,could rid myself of my long-standing \Nenemy in such a manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.08,CRZero,Esmile,0000,0000,0000,,Send the troops there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.10,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,It's been sealed with \Nthe power of sprites.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.69,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,No sword will open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:30.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.77,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Maddarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.44,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,You came just at the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:47.02,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,I had been forced to play along with
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:48.74,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Lukshana's crazy demands again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:51.39,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Please take these barbarians \Nback to their cell already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.35,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Ari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.28,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Maddarf, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.55,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,I have orders to kill the demon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.19,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,and those who consort with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.70,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Derf, we're breaking through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.48,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.13,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,It will only fuel the flames of hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.47,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.92,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna chase them all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:22.54,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:24.81,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.15,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:40.89,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.60,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,We've been ambushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:45.10,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Our speed is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:48.74,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, the engine's power is waning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.57,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,It can't handle any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:52.97,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.07,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:55.72,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,But, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:59.41,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can outrun \Ntheir fleet at this speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.85,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop the ship and \Nsee how they respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:05.17,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Miss Vallière!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.12,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I can take down the elven ships \Nwith my Explosion spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.36,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Taking down those ships \Nwill serve no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.59,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,It's far more dangerous to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.04,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,reveal to them that you are a Void Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.03,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta, please take Miss \NVallière somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.00,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:27.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:37.11,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,Mists of Sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:43.23,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.26,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,He's copying Ari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:47.23,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, please help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.08,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.22,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:14.67,CRZero,Elves,0000,0000,0000,,They're over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:15.70,CRZero,Elves,0000,0000,0000,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:17.49,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Turn into a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.33,CRZero,Elves,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.26,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,Are these all the people on the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.17,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really expect to face \Nus with this band of children?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.10,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Our only objective was to rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.11,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,our friends who were \Nabducted by you elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.78,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've fulfilled that objective, \Nwe will return home at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.17,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,Abducted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.51,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:47.29,CRZero,Elf,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.81,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it to the desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.64,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,but is this as far as we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.60,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No. I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:03.41,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I won't rest until I \Nsee you again, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:06.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito... Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.48,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Even my uncle's magic is \Nnot powerful enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:16.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.39,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.82,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,Once I break a hole in that wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:27.29,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fill it with poisonous gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.63,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Poisonous gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.89,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, we're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:34.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,We can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.99,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to believe \Nthat it will work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:40.76,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will see Louise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:42.69,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:48.25,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saito... Saito... Saito... Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.24,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:55.45,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:01.76,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:09.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, gyolf, hagaras... \NSoyl, beorc, daeg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.20,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.96,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Son, wyad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:31.45,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:34.89,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito... Saito, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.33,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.16,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.24,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.74,CRZero,Loise,0000,0000,0000,,My power is being replenished...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:56.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:02.20,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, I missed you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.62,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you too, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.73,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa, come on. Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.26,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.82,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.87,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I guess the relief got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.77,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can we come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.67,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay here, we'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.39,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.33,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Lukshana, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:29.17,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,We can't ask barbarians for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.41,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,Say your prayers, demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:34.05,CRZero,Maddarf,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.16,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we can't \Nconfirm whether your
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.26,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,story about this abduction \Nis true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.66,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll have to take \Nyou into custody and—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:48.61,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, it is the truth, Raiid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.40,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Master Bidalsha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.09,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.38,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm filled with pride to \Nsee that one of my students
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.05,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,has risen to the rank of captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.73,CRZero,Raiid,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.41,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell you the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:04.60,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,At the consideration
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.80,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,of our past as teacher and student,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.59,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I ask that you let this ship go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:16.68,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa, I'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.51,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was so worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:20.77,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.77,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did you get Saito and Tiffa out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.62,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.03,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I was wishing really hard \Nthat I could see Saito again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.43,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,when suddenly something \Nlike a window opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.29,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked on the other \Nside, Saito was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.48,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,This must be some new Void magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:38.48,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when I grabbed Saito's hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:41.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,it felt as if power was flowing into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.99,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I was glowing back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:47.83,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I've become \NTiffa's familiar, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I got these runes on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.42,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, can you tell me what this says?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:52.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Now hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:56.41,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You became Tiffa's familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:58.38,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So that means you k-k-k-ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:59.30,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Kissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:01.29,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That is what that means, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:01.93,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:03.30,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:06.38,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we did,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:08.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not what's \Nimportant right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.68,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.82,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Back in Adil, we're wanted people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:16.43,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's not go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:19.79,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay on this ship and go \Nto the barbarians' country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.01,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.61,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:24.39,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea. You should do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.26,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,You, too? You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:30.00,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,They won't follow you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.24,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,I will go back to Adil,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:33.94,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,but I will stay underground for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.38,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:38.23,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:43.07,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you wouldn't cheat on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.59,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,And you've already got me for a lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:46.71,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.39,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're not listening to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:52.42,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid perv dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:29.42,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito was supposed to be my \Nfamiliar, but now you're telling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:31.50,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,me he's Tiffa's familiar, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:34.56,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that's reason enough \Nto get all cozy with Tiffa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:36.16,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: \NTabitha's Coronation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:40.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I am your number one master!
